隙缓缓旋转，如同一只沉睡巨兽微微张开的眼睛。\\n[输出]\\nrole_type:\\nspeaker:\\nmotive:\\nawait_user:\\nnext_role_type:\\nnext_speaker:\\nchapter_outcome:\\nnext_chapter_id:\\nmemory_hints:\\ntrigger_memory_agent:\\nevent_facts:\\nstate_delta:\"}]}"}
